Strategically located within the Jandakot Airport Precinct, just off Roe Highway and the Kwinana Freeway, 20km* from the Perth CBD and 30km* from Fremantle Port, This property represents a unique opportunity within the WA market and boasts the following features:

- As new ‘AAA’ corporate facility
- Well designed and immaculately presented modern office and high truss warehouse with canopies
- Extensive secure parking and laydown areas
- Full drive around access
- Under cover wash down facility

*approx

Ideally situated in on the junction of two major freeways - the Kwinana Freeway and Roe Highway, Jandakot City provides superb and easy access to all parts of Western Australia while being approximately 15 minutes from both the Perth CBD and Fremantle.

The premises sits along WA’s premier 24 hour supermarket Spudshed and is exposed to a huge amount of footfall every day. Secure this 595sqm* premises within this modern mixed-use development which accommodates an array of national and local tenants.

Please contact your exclusive listing agents for more detail.

*Approx.

CBRE have pleasure offering for lease this substantial industrial facility located within the Jandakot Airport Estate.

Located on Marriott Road this exceptional facility includes 1,015sqm* of "A" Grade offices 10,920sqm* of quality high truss factory/warehouse and 4,218sqm* of laydown/yard area fully secured.

Rarely does a building of this quality become available for lease with quality fittings, excellent on-site parking and staff amenities.

*approx

Excellent opportunity to co-locate within a pre-existing successful business active in the tourism industry. Facility features excellent quality office/amenities, immaculate hangar with apron and excellent car parking.

Ideal for aviation based business or non-aviation business looking for office and storage space in an excellent location with easy access to freeways and Roe Highway
 
- Office $135/sqm pa + GST and variable outgoings
- Hangar $55/sqm pa + GST and variable outgoings
- Portion of apron and car parking included
 
Flexible allocation based on between 30% and 50% of the total facility which incorporates a total office area of 108sqm* and a total hangar area of 589sqm*.


*approx
